"{\"uid\": \"themarysue.com-tom-cruise-to-do-the-most-tom-cruise-thing-to-close-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"With all the stunts that Tom Cruise has pulled off in the course of theMission: Impossiblemovies, you'd think he could just be an honorary Olympian.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 139, \"end\": 147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999939301922082, \"rank\": 6.050054190434037e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have you seen the man run?\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, the 2024 Paris Olympics is giving him a chance to participate, but not in the way you think.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise is going to be doing the one thing he is an absolutely maverick at-a stunt to close the Paris Olympics and complete the ceremonial handoff of the flag to Los Angeles, which will host the 2028 Olympics!\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999995086455, \"rank\": 4.905396919091442e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, could there by anything more L.A. than one of the biggest movie stars we have pull of a stunt that is pure cinema?\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999992504172, \"rank\": 5.4388406388029685e-09, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ATMZ exclusivebroke the news that the 62-year-oldTop Gun: Maverickstar will perform a stunt to close the Paris Olympics, which will involve a a few bits, some of which will be live, with the others pre-recorded.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the report, Cruise is going to rappel down from the top of the Stade de France stadium onto the field while carrying the Olympic flag.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The live broadcast will then cut to a pre-recorded clip that will show him flying from France to Los Angeles on a plane, and then skydiving down to the Hollywood sign in L.A.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5870731766486521, \"rank\": 0.6092606429597428, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999995086455, \"rank\": 4.905396919091442e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999992504172, \"rank\": 5.4388406388029685e-09, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will then pass on the flag to another, and then as is tradition, it will pass down to other Olympians as they herald the 2028 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it turns out, the skydiving portion of the video has already been filmed way back in March, when Tom Cruise was spotted by paparazzi shooting a stunt over at the Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\